-	  serial port interface. You will also need this driver if you have 
-	  UART based Bluetooth PCMCIA and CF devices like Xircom Credit Card 
+	  serial port interface. You will also need this driver if you have
+	  UART based Bluetooth PCMCIA and CF devices like Xircom Credit Card
